[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說放牛經",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後秦龜茲國三藏鳩摩羅什譯",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，婆伽婆在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "園。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，佛告諸比丘：",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「有十一法，放牛兒不知放牛便宜，不曉養牛。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等十一？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a18_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者放牛兒不知色，二者不知相，三者不知摩刷，四者不知護瘡，五者不知作烟，六者不知擇道行，七者不知愛牛，八者不知何道渡水，九者不知逐好水草，十者𤛓牛不遺殘，十一者不知分別養可用不可用。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是十一事，放牛兒不曉養護其牛者，牛終不滋息，日日有減。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知行十一事，如放牛兒者，終不成沙門，此法中終不種法律根栽，無有葉枝覆蔭；",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不行十一事強為沙門者，死墮三惡道。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等比丘十一行？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘不知色，不知相，應摩刷不知摩刷，應護瘡不知護瘡，應作烟不知作烟，不知擇道行，不知愛牛，不知何道渡水，不知食處，不知敬長老。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何不知色？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知四大，不知四大所造色，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是不知。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b03_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何不知相？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知癡因緣相、不知黠因緣相。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何不知癡因緣相？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知黑緣，不知白緣，不知黑白緣。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何不知黠相？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知黑緣，不知白緣，不知白黑緣。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是不知相。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何應摩刷而不摩刷？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設欲心發便樂著，不捨、不忘、不斷絕，起愚癡貪慳及餘惡心，盡懷不吐捨。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應摩刷而不摩刷也。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何應護瘡而不護瘡？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見色起想、聞聲愛著，思想形體不知為惡，不護眼根、耳、鼻、舌、身、心，盡馳外塵而不能護。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b13_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應護瘡而不護瘡。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應作烟而不作烟？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所學聞不知為人說。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應起烟而不起烟。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知擇道行？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不入直道行，行於非道。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何行非道？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "入婬女里及酒會博戲處。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b18_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為不知行道。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘不知愛？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b19_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "講說法寶時，不至心愛樂聽。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為不知愛。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b20_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知渡水？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知四諦。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等四諦？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知苦諦、苦習諦、苦盡諦、苦盡道諦。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為不知渡水。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知食處？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知四意止。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等四意止？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b24_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知內觀身、外觀身、內外觀身，不知內觀痛、外觀痛、內外觀痛，不知內觀意、外觀意、內外觀意，不知內觀法、外觀法、內外觀法。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為不知食處。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知食不盡？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設為國王長者清信士女請食，設種種餚饌至心進上，比丘不知齊限，食已有餘復欲持歸。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為不知食不盡。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c02_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知敬長老？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "恭敬供養之云何不知？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設有長老比丘，久習道德學問廣博，小比丘不至心禮敬，見之不起不為避坐，輕慢調戲不以善心待。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知敬長老。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其有比丘，不知行十一法，於吾法中不應為沙門，不種法律根栽，無枝葉覆蔭皆自朽壞，不如還為白衣。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若強為沙門者必入三惡道。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知放牛兒十一行養護，其能使滋息。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何十一？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此放牛兒為：",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知色，知相，摩刷，護瘡，起烟，擇道，渡水，愛牛，逐水草，𤛓知遺殘齊限多少，分別牛好惡，養視可用者。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是放牛者，便能養護增益其牛。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛於是頌曰：",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「放牛兒審諦，　　牛主有福德，",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六頭牛六年，　　成六十不減。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "放牛兒聰明，　　知分別諸相，",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如此放牛兒，　　先世佛所譽。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是十一法，比丘當行，便能於是法中種法律根栽，枝葉茂盛覆蔭大地，不復朽壞。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等十一？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘知色、知相、知摩刷、知覆瘡、知時作烟、知行道、知愛、知渡水、知食處、知不盡、知敬長老舊學耆艾恭敬供養。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘知色？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知四大造起色，如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為知色。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c24_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘知相？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "別癡別黠。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何癡？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非所思而思、非所行而行、非所說而說，是為癡。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為黠？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "思可思、行可行、說可說，是為黠。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c27_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能別癡黠，是為知相。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘應摩刷知摩刷？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0546c28_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設生欲心能制遠避如吐惡見，設起瞋恚慳貪及餘諸惡，能制遠避如吐惡見。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a01_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應刷知刷。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘應護瘡而護？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眼見色不分別好惡、守護眼根不著外色、遠捨諸惡護於眼根，耳聽聲、鼻嗅香、舌嗜味、身貪細滑意多念，制不令著，護此諸根不染外塵如吐惡見。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為知護瘡。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘時時放烟？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所學所聞所知，以是廣說，如是比丘為知放烟。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘知行道？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘行審諦八道，知不可行處，婬里、酒家、博戲處，終不妄入，如是比丘為知行道。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘知愛？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見說法寶時，至心聽受踊躍愛樂，如是比丘名為知愛。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘知渡水處？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知四諦。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何四諦？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "苦諦、苦習諦、苦盡諦、苦盡道諦。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是比丘為知渡水。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘知食處？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知四意止。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何四意止？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a15_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀內身、觀外身、觀內外身，觀內痛、觀外痛、觀內外痛，觀內意觀、外意觀、內外意，觀內法、觀外法、觀內外法，如是比丘為知食處。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘知食不盡？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若國王長者清信士女，以信樂心請於比丘，供養飲食種種餚饌，加敬進勸，比丘知節供身則止，思惟佛語：",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『施者雖豐，當自知限，不為盡受。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』如是比丘知食不盡。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何比丘知敬長老舊學耆艾恭敬供養？",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當親近是輩禮敬供養，出入迎逆見來避坐，任力進上，勿以懈慢。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是比丘知，敬長老。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能行是十一事者，於此法中種法律根栽枝葉滋茂，多所覆蔭清淨無垢。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊以偈頌曰：",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「有信精進學，　　受食知節限，",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "恭敬於長老，　　是行佛稱譽。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547b01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如此十一法，　　比丘學是者，",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "晝夜定心意，　　六年得羅漢。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547b03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜受行。",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547b04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說放牛經",
        "from": "T02n0123_001:0547b05_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]